    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This beauty is in flawless condition\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with maintenance, keeping it garaged and pampered since day one. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44900.0,
