    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly breathtaking, showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating that highlights the deep luster of the paint with zero swirl marks, dings, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, the carpets are pristine, and it has been kept in a strictly smoke-free, climate-controlled environment. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full service history with all preventive maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the high-fidelity surround sound, operates with factory precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been garage-kept since day one and never driven in inclement weather. Truly a collector-grade find for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
